headline.print_headline: State Media: Car Bomb in Central Syria Kills 7
headline.main: State Media: Car Bomb in Central Syria Kills 7

lead_paragraph: A car bomb exploded Sunday in the central Syrian city of Homs, killing at least seven people, the country's state news agency reported.
